<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id779570a9-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s430h–8"><num value="430h–8">§ 430h–8.</num><heading> Park interpretation</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">In administering Vicksburg National Military Park, the Secretary shall interpret the campaign and siege of Vicksburg from April 1862 to <date date="1863-07-04">July 4, 1863</date>, and the history of Vicksburg under Union occupation during the Civil War and Reconstruction.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id779570aa-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">(<ref href="/us/pl/101/442/tI/s103">Pub. L. 101–442, title I, § 103</ref>, <date date="1990-10-18">Oct. 18, 1990</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/104/1020">104 Stat. 1020</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
